Date: 2002-06-07

Title: The Invariant Charges of the Nambu-Goto String Theory

Non-Additive Composition LawsAuthors: K. Pohlmeyer and M. Trunk

Comments: 23 pages LaTeX

We examine and implement the concept of non-additive composition laws in thequantum theory of closed bosonic strings moving in (3+1)-dimensional Minkowskispace. Such laws supply exact selection rules for the merging and splitting ofclosed strings.